    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h2><p>基于 nodejs , 略</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>安装hexo<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>初始化一个hexo目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;dir&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>安装hexo-deployer-git,支持git上传,本地支持github<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &lt;div&gt; &amp;&amp; npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在<code>&lt;dir&gt;</code>目录下找到<code>_config.yml</code>，修改<code>deploy</code>,配置git上传目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:xxx/xxx.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>发布文章<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建页面：hexo new post &quot;文章名字（可以是中文）&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">生成html ： hexo generate（或者hexo g）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">发布到git： hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">生成并发布：hexo generate -d （或者hexo g -d）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="修改主题"><a href="#修改主题" class="headerlink" title="修改主题"></a>修改主题</h2><p>下载主题到<code>&lt;dir&gt;\themes</code><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/frostfan/hexo-theme-polarbear</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在<code>_config.yml</code>中修改主题<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: polarbear</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
